{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the first comment was made about a school in Northbrook where this lady found toilet paper on the floor-- oh, the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I am a Jew, how can you say that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anybody can throw toilet paper on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the woman turned around and she said, oh, no, no, I'm part Jew also, you know, a little percent Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's just an example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My ears are open to any kind of accusation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If my friends make any kind of comment, they won't now because they know how I feel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When my children went to school, I identified myself as being Jewish-- convert, but being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my friends now sometimes make comments about they're tired of hearing of, you know, Holocaust survivors telling their story, other people perished here in this, I say yes, they did.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this, you know, I don't argue with them, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just make the point, yes, others did, but the Jews were [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] selected in a very, very large number with the purpose of totally annihilating them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I try, I try to say what I can here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But because they're my friends, it hurts that they should feel this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I wouldn't have done this tape if it hadn't been [SOBBING] that I want my children to always remember where they came from.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I never want any group to say that it never happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CRYING] And I'm very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
